}
#WgtRegNo3Class #labelInfo,#WgtRegNo4Class #labelInfo,#WgtVerifyNo3Class #labelInfo,#WgtVerifyNo4Class #labelInfo,#WgtRegNo3Class #spinBoxGMarked,#WgtRegNo3Class #spinBoxAllMarked
